{"word":"H7392 - רָכַב - râkab - raw-kab' - Bring","slug":"H7392","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">רָכַב</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>râkab"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>raw-kab'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Bring"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05E8;&#x05DB;&#x05D1; - ra&#x0302;kab</b> - <i>raw-kab'</i><p/>A primitive root; to <i>ride</i> (on an animal or in a vehicle); causatively to <i>place upon</i> (for riding or generally), to <i>despatch: - </i>bring (on [horse-] back), carry, get [oneself] up, on [horse-] back, put, (cause to, make to) ride (in a chariot, on, -r), set."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H4817\">H4817</a>, <a href=\"#/H4818\">H4818</a>, <a href=\"#/H7393\">H7393</a>, <a href=\"#/H7394\">H7394</a>, <a href=\"#/H7395\">H7395</a>, <a href=\"#/H7396\">H7396</a>, <a href=\"#/H7397\">H7397</a>, <a href=\"#/H7398\">H7398</a>"}]}